    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>[In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritus Sancti. Regnante Heinrico rege filio
                        quondam Heinrici imperatoris anno] quarto, sub an[no dominice]
                        [inca]rn[acionis] millesimo se[xa]g[esimo], di[e] quarta mensis marcii,
                        [in]dic(ione) tertja[decima], <placeName ref="#places/594" key="#Cities"
                            >RAV(enne)</placeName>. [Pecii a te in Dei nomin]e d[om]no <persName
                            key="#Monks"><name ref="Wido">Wid[on]e</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">[mona]cho</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Rivers #Price #Penalty #Books #Rent_in_money #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">[Sancte] Marie [in] <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomp[osea</placeName></orgName>, ad a]firmandum a
                        domno [...] [...] ad[que <rs key="#Abbots">a]bb[ate]</rs> ei[usdem
                        monasterii cum] consensu mona[c]horum [ipsi monasterii], uti [me] presenti
                        in Christ[i] nomine <persName><name ref="Petrus Mangagnolus">Pe[trus
                                Mangagn]olus</name></persName> [p]etitori pro me et pro
                                <persName><name ref="Berta">Ber[ta</name></persName> ......] [...] −
                        si quis de nobis petitoris sine [filio vel filia] [moritur] eius porcio
                        veniat [i]lli qui [supravixeri]t − <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            >lib[e]ll[i] nomine</rs> concedisti nobis rem iuris suprascripto
                        monasterio Pompos[iano], [idest cu]biculum unum in integrum de una <rs
                            key="#Houses">mansione pedeplana</rs>, extensum <rs key="#Size">in longo
                            pedibus treginta et [in] lato pedibus de[cem]</rs>, cum porcione ripe
                            <rs key="#Rivers">fluminis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/3558">Teguriense</placeName>, cum
                        ingr(essu) et regr(essu) suo atque cum omnibus sibi pertinentibus, positum
                        in hac <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> Ravenne, regione ********** <rs
                            key="#Confinia">interraffines</rs> eius: a primo latere tenet domno
                            <persName key="#Confinia #Priests"><name ref="Hugo"
                            >Ugone</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> iure suprascripto monasterio, a secundo
                        latere <rs key="#Confinia #Fruits/vegetables">ortum vestrum domnicatum</rs>,
                        a tercio latere <rs key="#Confinia #Walls">murum</rs> istius civitatis atque
                        a qu[arto latere] <rs key="#Confinia #Roads">plathea plubica</rs>
                        percurrens. Habendum, tenen[dum, possi]dendum, restaurandum, meliorandum, in
                        annis [adveni]entibus viginti et novem ad renovandum, sub pe[nsione omni]
                        anno <rs key="#Rent_in_money">den(arios) Ven(eticos) viginti et
                            quattuor</rs> [tantum et amis]seres duos. Pro eo quia accepisti in
                        [m]a[num tuam de ma]no mea, call(ciarii) nomine, idest <rs key="#Books"
                            >librum</rs> unum pro <rs key="#Price">den(ariorum) V[eneticorum
                            solidis] treginta</rs>. Et vos cum vestris successoribus [nobis
                        petito]ribus nostrisque filiis auctoriare et defensare promit|[ti]stis. Si
                        quis vero partis nostre contra hanc petitionem ire tentaverit ante
                        p(re)finitum tempus quod superius legitur, det pars parti fidem servanti
                        ANTE omne litis initium [aut] interpell(acionem), pene nomine, <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi uncia una</rs> et post pene soluc(ionem)
                        maneat hec peticio firma. QUAm vero peticio <persName key="#Tabellio"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannem</name></persName> Dei misericordia Ravennas
                            <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellionem</rs> scrib[en]d[um] [r]ogavi, sub die
                        menseque et anno atque indic(ione) suprascripta t[erciadecima,
                        RAV(enne)(a)]. [+] Signum + manus Petri Mangagnolo peti[t]oris [ad omnia
                        suprascripta].</ab>
